highlights.text: KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Norway. “Golden” is the highest at #14.
“No Broke Boys” by Disco Lines and Tinashe has been on Viral Songs Norway the longest, at 83 days straight.
“Purpose” by J.R.A is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Norway at #33.
“The Night The Lights Went Out In Georgia” by Reba McEntire is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Norway, up 20 spots at #41.
